{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "DOP/surfacecollisionparms", "tags": "cloth"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Volume Collider"], "extent": [47, 67]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Create a Static Object from SOP Geometry pre-configured for interaction with cloth."], "extent": [67, 159]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [159, 174], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool is used for a static object that influences a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/clothobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Cloth Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/clothobject"}, ". It is similar to the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/shelf/clothbodycollider", "type": "link", "text": ["Surface Collider"], "fullpath": "/shelf/clothbodycollider"}, ", the main difference being that the Deforming Collider interacts with polygons and the Volume Collider interacts with volumes. "], "extent": [174, 462]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["You should use a ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/shelf/clothbodycollider", "type": "link", "text": ["Surface Collider"], "fullpath": "/shelf/clothbodycollider"}, " if your static object is moving around and colliding with cloth, such as for the body of a character interacting with clothing. You should use a Volume Collider if your object is not deforming, for example for a terrain that a cloth object is interacting with."], "extent": [462, 793]}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Using Volume Collider"], "extent": [793, 821], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Select the geometry to convert to a static object."], "extent": [821, 884]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "DOP/surfacecollisionparms", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/DOP/surfacecollisionparms"}, {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/staticobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Volume Collider"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/staticobject"}, " tool on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Cloth"]}, " or ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Solid"]}, " tab."], "extent": [884, 1013]}], "container": true}, {"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 4, "text": [" "], "role": "item", "extent": [1013, 1024], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["You can ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/basics/handles", "type": "link", "text": ["transform, rotate, scale"], "fullpath": "/basics/handles"}, ", and ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/anim/basics", "type": "link", "text": ["keyframe"], "fullpath": "/anim/basics"}, " the static object at various frames."], "extent": [1024, 1150]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The following example is an organic tissue object falling down a staircase."], "extent": [1150, 1227]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/shelf/rigidcollider.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "extent": [1227, 1268]}, {"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"type": "tip", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [1268, 1273], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["When using volume-based collisions, only the cloth points collide with the volume. If you want more accurate collisions, disable ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Volume Based Collisions"]}, " on the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/staticobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Static Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/staticobject"}, ". "], "extent": [1273, 1490]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [1490, 1499], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/clothobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Cloth Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/clothobject"}], "extent": [1499, 1541]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdobject"}], "extent": [1541, 1579]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/staticsolver", "type": "link", "text": ["Static Solver"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/staticsolver"}], "extent": [1579, 1623]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/groundplane", "type": "link", "text": ["Ground Plane"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/groundplane"}], "extent": [1623, 1665]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/terrainobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Terrain Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/terrainobject"}], "extent": [1665, 1710]}], "container": true}], "text": "Related"}], "title": ["Volume Collider"], "summary": ["Create a Static Object from SOP Geometry pre-configured for interaction with cloth."]}